To maximise our impact on Europen Union's policies, Autism-Europe works in strategic coalitions with organisations that share the same concerns and goals. &#xd;
&#xd;
These include the European Disability Forum (EDF), the Platform of European Social NGOs and the European Coalition for Community Living (ECCL). Autism-Europe is a founder member of these organisations and currently holds the vice presidency of the European Disability Forum.
